ygData.messageBody:
Ok Ive posted the player list into my homepage already. If there's any
mistakes pls email me. Also if anyone's name is not inside, pls pls lemme
know abt it. Anyone with websites or guild websites related to Singapore
online gaming(dont have to be EQ) give me the URL I'll add them. Already
added HOS and AdV into list and need more.
Does anyone know where I can find Singaporeans playing UO or EQ? Is there a
mailing list or messageboard which Singaporeans Frequent? Since I already
made a player list for Eq I might as well make one for UO and AC as well so
that if someday a new online game come out can contact them easier :)
SPECIAL: Go to http://home.pacific.net.sg/~dexterwong/friends.html and send
it to your friends. You'll be suprised how many true friends you have!
